Package boardgraphics

Contains user interface independent functionality for displaying a board on a sccreen.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Drawable
    items to be drawn by the functions in GraphicsContext must implement this interface
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColorIntensityTable
    The color intensities for each item type.
    ColorTableModel
    Abstract class to store colors used for drawing the board.
    CoordinateTransform
    Transformation function between the board and the screen coordinate systems.
    GraphicsContext
    Context for drawing items in the board package to the screen.
    ItemColorTableModel
    Stores the layer dependent colors used for drawing for the items on the board.
    ItemDrawInfo
    Information for drawing an item on the screen.
    OtherColorTableModel
    Stores the colors used for the background and highlighting.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ColorIntensityTable.ObjectNames
